{"tid":747092,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「一個泳圈」測出有多瘦！　子瑜伸手套…成員驚呆：喔喔喔 原文網址: 「一個泳圈」測出有多瘦！","createTime":"2018-07-18T06:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T08:40:15.000Z","uid":51412,"like":10,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc875a796c682cb3032a9c037242ae77cc40398","tid":747092,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"韓女團TWICE近日以新歌《Dance The Night Away》回歸，MV特別到沖繩海邊取景，相當符合夏季風格，拍攝當天的花絮影片也陸續釋出，其中一段子瑜套上青蛙泳圈的影片，格外讓粉絲哭笑不得，只見她身體才剛泡水泡一半，便忍不住失控高八度尖叫，彩瑛和定延在一旁看了都驚呆：「什麼啊？！害怕什麼啊？！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420516.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420516.jpg&h=7c8ba6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼TWICE為了MV換上泳裝入鏡。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420517.jpg&h=b021a673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始可以看到穿著黃色泳衣的彩瑛套上泳圈，幾乎整個身體都泡在淺水裡，玩得不亦樂乎，興奮地直尖叫，吸引定延也湊過去說想玩，兩個女孩都很享受海水的清涼，輪到子瑜套好泳圈後，下半身才剛泡進去水裡就用韓文說：「我好害怕。」接著開始驚聲尖叫，一邊握住成員的手，一邊趕快站起來，成員們看了都笑說：「膽小鬼！膽小鬼！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420505.jpg&h=e57fb54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼子瑜剛泡進水裡就失控尖叫。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420512.jpg&h=f8c1a817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420513.jpg&h=346ba889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼子瑜連忙起身露出害羞笑容。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420515.jpg&h=f204a10e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，子瑜這次破尺度換上泳裝入鏡，身穿紅色碎花圖案的泳衣，搭配牛仔短褲，準備套泳圈前，雙手一舉高，泳圈輕鬆套入身體，可見她的身型有多麼纖瘦，連彩瑛和定延看了都忍不住驚呼：「喔喔喔喔！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420506.jpg&h=6bf0b2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼子瑜伸手套泳圈。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420508.jpg&h=7e7aa09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3420/d3420510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3420%2Fd3420510.jpg&h=bae4af6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4242f6a7f112e4acb49a4a6b64f5914185949482","tid":747092,"uid":2419,"like":1397,"dislike":48,"score":1349,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.4plebs.org/boards/s4s/image/1489/67/1489679987623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4plebs.org%2Fboards%2Fs4s%2Fimage%2F1489%2F67%2F1489679987623.jpg&h=1e30bf0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77829d48b5e6fdfddef2f3505381567edbb6bc7c","tid":747092,"uid":20032,"like":73,"dislike":444,"score":-371,"quote":{"pid":"4242f6a7f112e4acb49a4a6b64f5914185949482","tid":747092,"uid":2419,"like":1397,"dislike":48,"score":1349,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.4plebs.org/boards/s4s/image/1489/67/1489679987623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4plebs.org%2Fboards%2Fs4s%2Fimage%2F1489%2F67%2F1489679987623.jpg&h=1e30bf0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"請尊重，謝謝！"},{"pid":"26a6305fd0bad9e96e5afd522443d94438af4fa1","tid":747092,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"ci